<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<title><%= title %></title>
<link href="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/twitter-bootstrap/2.3.2/css/bootstrap-combined.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
<script src="//ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script src="//netdna.bootstrapcdn.com/twitter-bootstrap/2.3.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
<style>
.installpage {width:530px;height:600px;border:2px solid;border-radius: 25px;}
</style>
<center><div class="installpage" align="center">
<br><h1>欢迎使用LightBlog！</h1><br>
<p>当你看到这个页面的时候，你应该已经设置好setiings.js了</p><br>
<p>现在，添加一个管理员账号，开始使用LightBlog吧！</p><br>
<form method="post" class="form-horizontal">
   <div class="control-group">
    <label class="control-label" for="name">用户名</label>
    <div class="controls">
      <input type="text" id="name" name="name">
    </div>
    <br>
    <label class="control-label" for="password">密码</label>
    <div class="controls">
      <input type="password" id="password" name="password">
    </div>
    <br>
    <label class="control-label" for="password-repeat">确认密码</label>
    <div class="controls">
      <input type="password" id="password-repeat" name="password-repeat">
    </div>
    <br>
    <label class="control-label" for="email">邮箱</label>
    <div class="controls">
      <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="与头像有关，请谨慎填写">
    </div>
    <br>
    <center>
    <button type="submit" class="btn">添加</button>
    </center>
  </div>
</form>
<div class="alert alert-block">
  <p><b>完成后请删除views里的install.ejs和route的index.js里的安装部分！</b></p>
</div>
</div>
</center>
<%- include footer %>